Class PantallaPrincipal

java.lang.Object
java.awt.Component

vista.principal.PantallaPrincipal
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class PantallaPrincipal
extends javax.swing.JPanel
Class that contains the components and functionalities to create a view for the main screen. From this view the user will be able to go through all the tabs of the application.
Author:
Pedro Rodriguez Urbina, Cesar Ramirez Martinez
